Part 4   Complete the conversation. (10 points)
A: Have you heard? Emily (1) _______________ just been offered a scholarship to study in Canada!
B: No way! When (2) _______________ she find out?
A: Just yesterday. She (3) _______________ apparently applied for it months ago.
B: That's incredible. If I (4) _______________ the chance, I would definitely study abroad too.
A: Would you? I'm (5) _______________ sure. I'd find it hard to leave my family.
B: I understand. But the opportunities would (6) _______________ been amazing though.
A: True. The university must (7) _______________ been very impressed by her application.
B: For sure. She's (8) _______________ worked so hard these past years.
A: I know. I really hope she (9) _______________ have to worry about money while she's there.
B: The scholarship covers everything, so she (10) _______________ have any financial concerns.
